{"sn36.12:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 36.12 ","sn36.12:0.2":"2. Rahogatavagga ","sn36.12:0.3":"Pathamaakasasutta ","sn36.12:1.1":"“Seyyathapi, bhikkhave, akase vividha vata vayanti. ","sn36.12:1.2":"Puratthimapi vata vayanti, pacchimapi vata vayanti, uttarapi vata vayanti, dakkhinapi vata vayanti, sarajapi vata vayanti, arajapi vata vayanti, sitapi vata vayanti, unhapi vata vayanti, parittapi vata vayanti, adhimattapi vata vayanti. ","sn36.12:1.3":"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, imasmim kayasmim vividha vedana uppajjanti, sukhapi vedana uppajjati, dukkhapi vedana uppajjati, adukkhamasukhapi vedana uppajjatiti. ","sn36.12:2.1":"Yathapi vata akase, ","sn36.12:2.2":"vayanti vividha puthu; ","sn36.12:2.3":"Puratthima pacchima capi, ","sn36.12:2.4":"uttara atha dakkhina. ","sn36.12:3.1":"Saraja araja capi, ","sn36.12:3.2":"sita unha ca ekada; ","sn36.12:3.3":"Adhimatta paritta ca, ","sn36.12:3.4":"puthu vayanti maluta. ","sn36.12:4.1":"Tathevimasmim kayasmim, ","sn36.12:4.2":"samuppajjanti vedana; ","sn36.12:4.3":"Sukhadukkhasamuppatti, ","sn36.12:4.4":"adukkhamasukha ca ya. ","sn36.12:5.1":"Yato ca bhikkhu atapi, ","sn36.12:5.2":"sampajannam na rincati; ","sn36.12:5.3":"Tato so vedana sabba, ","sn36.12:5.4":"parijanati pandito. ","sn36.12:6.1":"So vedana parinnaya, ","sn36.12:6.2":"ditthe dhamme anasavo; ","sn36.12:6.3":"Kayassa bheda dhammattho, ","sn36.12:6.4":"sankhyam nopeti vedagu”ti. ","sn36.12:6.5":"Dutiyam. "}